          <p>
            Any use of the Software in a commercial context — including use by for-profit companies, freelancers billing clients,
            or any activity that generates revenue — requires a paid commercial license purchased through our Website or authorized reseller.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">Commercial licenses are available in the following tiers:</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 ml-4 list-disc space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Individual</strong> — $19 one-time, 1 developer, 1 year of updates. Optional renewal: $9/year.</li>
            <li><strong>Team</strong> — $49 one-time, up to 5 developers, 1 year of updates. Optional renewal: $29/year.</li>
            <li><strong>Enterprise</strong> — $149/year, unlimited developers, continuous updates, priority support</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">
            See the <a href="/pricing" class="text-accent-text hover:underline">Pricing page</a> for full details.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-heading mt-4 mb-2">2.3 License Scope</h3>
          <p>
            Commercial licenses are perpetual for the version purchased. After the included update period expires,
            you may continue using your current version indefinitely. Renewal is optional and grants access to new releases.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">3. Purchases and Payments</h2>
          <p>
            Payments are processed by <a href="https://stripe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent-text hover:underline">Stripe</a>.
            By making a purchase, you also agree to
            <a href="https://stripe.com/legal/consumer" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent-text hover:underline">Stripe's Consumer Terms</a>.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
