          <p>
            To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, MyShows Inc. shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental,
            special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of profits or data, arising out of or related to your
            use of the Software, even if we have been advised of the possibility of such damages.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Our total liability for any claim arising from these Terms shall not exceed the amount you paid for the Software
            in the twelve (12) months preceding the claim.
